<item>
            <title>[HBASE-14294] Add new attribute to Scan to limit the return size of records</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-14294</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Reason:&lt;br/&gt;
we all use PageFilter to limit the size of the return records,but the PageFilter return limit * region number size of limit ,which is bad for a huge number of region per table.&lt;br/&gt;
Solution:&lt;br/&gt;
ClientScanner has a attribute caching which determine the return size of record per RPC,so we can use this attribute to limit the return size of hbase.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
